{"id":428413,"date":[{"year":1962,"month":3,"day":17}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"228","ytitle":"","mtitle":"工人新村","ftitle":"","authors":["谢其规"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"谢其规"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进新楼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摸过绿窗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又摸红墙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子的妈呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这可不是咱年轻时的梦想!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞧你这股子乐劲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——脸红得象当年做新娘……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你快过来看呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窗外一幅好景象:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工厂的烟囱碰蓝天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宽阔的长街飘花香……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嗨!你布置新房先别忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快帮我挂好毛主席象!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"傍晚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳漫步下山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汽笛渐细渐远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲人已经下班，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一辆辆汽车开到门前!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这家传出炒菜声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那家飘出饭香；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大嫂们温柔的笑脸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伸出了窗门、厨房……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑妞奔上去抱住爸爸的腿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁娃做好的习题递给哥哥看；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竹笛吹出幸福笑语，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"口琴吹出弯弯月亮……"}]}